bilingual.source: It is also unreasonable to attach psychiatric labels to isolated attempts at such contact.

bilingual.source: She is undergoing psychiatric treatment for her anxiety disorder.
bilingual.target: 她正在接受精神病学的治疗，以应对她的焦虑症。

bilingual.source: He decided to specialize in psychiatric medicine after medical school.
bilingual.target: 他在医学院毕业后决定专攻精神病学的医学。

bilingual.source: The psychiatric evaluation revealed underlying issues that needed attention.
bilingual.target: 精神病学的评估揭示了需要关注的潜在问题。

bilingual.source: The hospital has a psychiatric ward for patients with severe mental illnesses.
bilingual.target: 这家医院有一个精神病学的病房，专门收治重症精神病患者。

bilingual.source: The psychiatric conference discussed the latest advancements in mental health care.
bilingual.target: 精神病学的会议讨论了精神健康护理的最新进展。

bilingual.source: He has been transferred to a psychiatric hospital.
bilingual.target: 他已被转移到精神病院。
这主要是一种精神方面的问题。

bilingual.source: Some psychiatric patients also get chronic itch.
bilingual.target: 一些精神病人也有慢性骚痒。

bilingual.source: The study appeared in the June Psychiatric Services.
bilingual.target: 这项研究成果发表在六月的《精神病医疗服务》上。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd be happy to put him under a 72 hour Psychiatric hold.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很乐意把他送进监护病房进行72小时的精神病观察。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I mean, I was until I met Rita and now I'm just a "mechanic with psychiatric delusions."
yingyinNormal.zh: 那已经是遇见瑞塔之前的事了，现在我只是个精神有问题的机械师。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, moving to psychiatric disorders. List all major behavioral diagnoses, depression, anxiety, etc.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，下面是精神疾病的问题，列出所有重大行为方面的病症例如沮丧、焦虑等等。

yingyinNormal.en: Answer yes or no. Has there ever been, against my express instructions, any attempt at a psychiatric evaluation of Eurus Holmes?
yingyinNormal.zh: 回答是或不是，你们是否曾违反我的明确指令尝试对欧罗斯·福尔摩斯进行过精神鉴定。
